  "description": "Reverts the sounds of Pistons to the full volume pre 1.21 sounds",
  "body": "**About**:\n------------\n- This pack was made because I felt that the 24w20a piston sounds weren't particularly good, and that the original sounds were more appealing despite being quite loud.\n- 24w21a reverted the pistons to the original sound but at a lower volume, making this pack much less necessary.\n- for the sake of having a full volume version this pack will remain available here.\n\n\nall this pack changes are the two piston sounds.\n\nit should work with every version of minecraft after 1.20.6\n\n**My other work**:\n------------\n\n- [Gerudoku Faithful](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/gerudoku-faithful)\n\n- [Doku's RPG](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/dokus-rpg)\n\n- [Biome Color Removed](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/biome-color-removed)\n\n- [Classic Full Block Chest](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-full-block-chest)\n\n- [Better Cactus Flower](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-cactus-flower)",
